{"word":"Camel","slug":"camel","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Camel</b> Herds of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=12&verse=16'>Gen 12:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=35'>Gen 24:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=30&verse=43'>Gen 30:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=30&verse=17'>1Sa 30:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=27&verse=30'>1Ch 27:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=1&verse=3'>Job 1:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=1&verse=17'>Job 1:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=60&verse=6'>Isa 60:6</a><br/> Docility of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=11'>Gen 24:11</a><br/> Uses of:<br/> - For riding<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=10'>Gen 24:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=61'>Gen 24:61</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=64'>Gen 24:64</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=31&verse=17'>Gen 31:17</a> <br/> - For posts<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=8&verse=10'>Est 8:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=8&verse=14'>Est 8:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=2&verse=23'>Jer 2:23</a> <br/> - For drawing chariots<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=21&verse=7'>Isa 21:7</a> <br/> - For carrying burdens<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=10'>Gen 24:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=25'>Gen 37:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=2'>1Ki 10:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=8&verse=9'>2Ki 8:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=40'>1Ch 12:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=30&verse=6'>Isa 30:6</a> <br/> - For cavalry<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=30&verse=17'>1Sa 30:17</a> <br/> - For milk<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=32&verse=15'>Gen 32:15</a> <br/> Forbidden as food<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=11&verse=4'>Lev 11:4</a><br/> Hair of, made into cloth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=3&verse=4'>Mat 3:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=6'>Mar 1:6</a><br/> Ornaments of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=8&verse=21'>Jdg 8:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=8&verse=26'>Jdg 8:26</a><br/> Stables for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=25&verse=5'>Eze 25:5</a>"}]}